"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/18/1036-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-18 10:36#[bugfix] ComfyUI: Fix NotImplementedError for Float8_e4m3fn in CUDA operations: The user encountered a `NotImplementedError` in ComfyUI when attempting to use the SamplerCustomAdvanced node. The error message, `\"mul_cuda\" not implemented for 'Float8_e4m3fn'`, indicates that a specific CUDA operation required for multiplication is not supported for the `Float8_e4m3fn` data type. This prevented the sampler from executing correctly. The error originates within the custom sampler nodes, specifically during the `sample` method call which eventually leads to a CUDA operation that lacks support for this particular floating-point format.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"9p17h","at":1782088665564},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.00816677,-0.01381574,0.02352056,-0.04429727,-0.00099439,-0.00933191,-0.07842866,-0.00201841,0.00670449,-0.01953265,0.01730728,-0.05624105,0.00600148,0.0287895,0.02076188,0.06465933,-0.03960905,0.02791529,0.04104577,0.04651679,0.07205928,0.00700635,0.00887827,-0.02146234,0.0219235,0.05276791,-0.023597,-0.09570226,-0.05322781,-0.27577019,0.00577463,0.00402787,0.06462254,-0.04418736,0.03979019,-0.06730156,-0.03722484,0.01005913,0.049459,0.05372345,-0.02504749,0.04682283,-0.0450383,-0.01936238,0.02818325,-0.00055715,-0.04127418,-0.00373613,0.0628313,-0.03833782,-0.03142962,-0.01887402,-0.01523778,0.01082426,0.0004383,0.06861635,-0.00191276,-0.0262855,0.03469058,0.06481109,0.06178556,0.02969852,-0.18141808,0.05428541,0.04905872,-0.01141568,0.04368356,-0.05030878,0.06507263,0.05532442,-0.04907218,-0.01646921,0.01161067,0.03487954,-0.01221391,0.00805953,-0.00100025,-0.0392867,-0.01219494,-0.01563608,0.01695286,0.00337984,-0.01118663,0.00097568,0.0349934,-0.0419967,-0.00785555,0.00362554,0.04758928,0.02812872,-0.02095801,-0.00291962,-0.04732861,0.06750578,-0.03411551,0.00546251,0.07616466,0.02731629,-0.10840805,0.09801342,-0.0110677,-0.011