"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/18/1036-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-18 10:36#[discovery] ARSESP IDP Pipeline Status Audit: The ARSESP IDP pipeline is currently in an early stage of ingestion and parsing. While uploads are progressing without failure, the parsing phase is lagging behind the upload volume. The system uses a structured set of tables in `nie_dev.ai_cortex` to track registry, checkpoints, and extracted entities. A known functional issue regarding OPEX vs CAPEX fleet analysis was resolved via prompt v3 on 2026-05-21. The immediate roadmap requires completing the upload batches and processing the parse backlog using `arsesp_ai_parse_batch_plan.py` and `arsesp_databricks_safe_executor.py` before enabling Vector Search and migrating the App Cortex to the new IDP base.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"8xefs1","at":1782088666021},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.09264832,-0.00229436,0.03193567,-0.10043336,-0.02257614,0.00036223,-0.02485963,0.00199047,-0.00301494,-0.01175841,0.04587344,-0.07059006,0.02299797,0.02972204,-0.06195189,0.05637695,0.00418724,-0.02279308,0.07039741,0.01328273,0.04270588,-0.03125976,-0.01677989,-0.02574616,-0.0125528,0.0836982,0.01047257,-0.06941567,-0.10108639,-0.2707262,0.0474837,-0.07883238,0.05483691,-0.04565601,-0.04156507,-0.00224287,-0.00951095,0.08043488,0.02162437,0.07417364,-0.00952592,-0.04455898,-0.06445602,-0.00371663,-0.02074017,-0.07267635,-0.02448247,-0.04054799,0.01853501,-0.04305611,-0.08904617,0.00444676,0.04454893,-0.00490321,0.01387107,0.02628476,0.00566194,-0.00785485,0.03533206,0.0522139,0.03965399,-0.03231053,-0.20344526,0.07835317,0.08662464,0.06288531,-0.081861,-0.04701054,0.02832763,0.01882108,-0.08507386,-0.00705817,0.01748985,0.05471529,-0.01068559,-0.01646143,0.06288898,0.01003889,-0.00598241,-0.03851969,0.01647051,0.00819481,0.00748718,-0.03400998,-0.00477587,-0.02542814,0.01919666,-0.01641379,0.06529181,0.01815446,0.00419611,0.04839477,0.00107717,0.02327555,-0.024