"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/18/1036-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-18 10:36#[change] Generated LLM Council Advisor Prompts: Five separate markdown files were generated, each containing a tailored prompt for a different LLM advisor role within a council. These roles include The Contrarian, The First Principles Thinker, The Expansionist, The Outsider, and The Executor. Each prompt clearly outlines the advisor's unique thinking style and provides the user's problem statement regarding the AI Hive Mind project in Obsidian. The goal is to elicit specific, focused advice from each advisor on architectural patterns for scalable memory consolidation, avoiding large file silos while maintaining discoverability. The prompts also enforce a direct communication style and word count limits.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"15xk7vr","at":1782088666209},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.093364,0.02060472,0.06274676,-0.03140239,-0.00981032,0.01667667,-0.03533901,-0.00261048,0.01606607,-0.06230357,0.025877,0.01176032,0.01902059,0.03083993,0.01374417,0.02411251,-0.03724019,-0.013667,0.04044599,0.05093084,0.07375667,-0.04770769,0.03583712,0.01339376,-0.0420262,-0.01500834,-0.02692999,-0.06505914,-0.09156138,-0.23057048,0.07675877,-0.00160031,0.04348511,0.00852642,-0.04170151,-0.02490257,-0.03614089,0.05234388,-0.0566475,0.05756289,-0.02524655,-0.0322399,-0.00575614,-0.00470955,-0.06285865,-0.08054805,-0.01253378,-0.03702674,-0.05907673,-0.04189143,-0.05872225,-0.03899775,-0.01089903,-0.03802009,0.03743739,0.00904834,0.03686657,0.0324677,0.06278133,0.06163242,0.07208182,0.01429826,-0.21823189,0.09690762,0.01089799,0.02580172,-0.05889389,0.01959905,0.03170785,0.04728462,-0.04353674,-0.01558446,0.02798601,0.0354541,0.04128,0.00699026,-0.05172005,0.00722028,0.0397573,-0.04616488,-0.03479088,-0.00931378,-0.03967127,-0.07788087,0.01327537,-0.01739304,-0.02467741,0.03237347,0.00262112,0.01880874,0.03138791,-0.00996638,-0.01227501,-0.00967663,-0.017307